e depleted in {\textless}span class="inline-formula"{\textgreater}$^{\textrm{13}}$C{\textless}/span{\textgreater}). Finally, our results suggest that marine emissions of methane from Arctic continental-shelf sources are dominated by thermogenic-origin methane, with a secondary biogenic source as well.{\textless}/p{\textgreater}},
