rmula"{\textgreater}$^{\textrm{−1}}${\textless}/span{\textgreater}, for a total anthropogenic CO{\textless}span class="inline-formula"{\textgreater}$_{\textrm{2}}${\textless}/span{\textgreater} emission of 10.2 {\textless}span class="inline-formula"{\textgreater}±{\textless}/span{\textgreater} 0.8 GtC yr{\textless}span class="inline-formula"{\textgreater}$^{\textrm{−1}}${\textless}/span{\textgreater} (37.4 {\textless}span class="inline-formula"{\textgreater}±{\textless}/span{\textgreater} 2.9 GtCO{\textless}span class="inline-formula"{\textgreater}$_{\textrm{2}}${\textless}/span{\textgreater}). Also, for 2020, {\textless}span class="inline-formula"{\textgreater}\textit{G}$_{\textrm{ATM}}${\textless}/span{\textgreater} was 5.0 {\textless}span class="inline-formula"{\textgreater}±{\textless}/span{\textgreater} 0.2 GtC yr{\textless}span class="inline-formula"{\textgreater}$^{\textrm{−1}}${\textless}/span{\textgreater} (2.4 {\textless}span class="inline-formula"{\textgreater}±{\textless}/span{\textgreater} 0.1 ppm yr{\textless}span class="inline-formula"{\textgreater}$^{\textrm{−1}}${\textless}/span{\textgreater}), {\textless}span class="inline-formula"{\textgreater}\textit{S}$_{\textrm{OCEAN}}${\textless}/span{\textgreater} was 3.0 {\textless}span class="inline-formula"{\textgreater}±{\textless}/span{\textgreater} 0.4 GtC yr{\textless}span class="inline-formula"{\textgreater}$^{\textrm{−1}}${\textless}/span{\textgreater}, and {\textless}span class="inline-formula"{\textgreater}\textit{S}$_{\textrm{LAND}}${\textless}/span{\textgreater} was 2.9 {\textless}span class="inline-formula"{\textgreater}±{\textless}/span{\textgreater} 1 GtC yr{\textless}span class="inline-formula"{\textgreater}$^{\textrm{−1}}${\textless}/span{\textgreater}, with a {\textless}span class="inline-formula"{\textgreater}\textit{B}$_{\textrm{IM}}${\textless}/span{\textgreater} of {\textless}span class="inline-formula"{\textgreater}−{\textless}/span{\textgreater}0.8 GtC yr{\textless}span class="inline-